%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22America%20isn't%20building%20enough%20homes.%20A%20new%20map%20may%20fix%20that.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Houses%20rising%20out%20of%20a%20map%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c526b8917a1dae024498e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAdri%C3%A1n%20Astorgano%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20who's%20doing%20the%20estimating%2C%20America%20is%20short%20anywhere%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-outlook-shortage-home-prices-mortgage-rates-real-estate-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E2%20million%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fbusiness%2F2023%2F01%2F25%2Fwhite-house-renter-protection%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E6%20million%20homes%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20you've%20tried%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzandi-moodys-house-prices-mortgage-interest-rates-affordability-crisis-market-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebuy%20or%20rent%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20place%20in%20the%20past%20year%2C%20or%20you%20know%20anyone%20who%20has%2C%20then%20you%20didn't%20need%20me%20to%20tell%20you%20that.%20Hardly%20anything's%20on%20the%20market%2C%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feconomic-inequality-housing-shortage-causes-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Enone%20of%20us%20can%20afford%20what%20is%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20question%20is%3A%20Why%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1177%2F00420980231159500%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esimple%20question%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20oddly%2C%20has%20been%20impossible%20to%20answer%20with%20any%20real%20precision.%20The%20housing%20shortage%20may%20be%20national%2C%20but%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-housing-market-home-price-outlook-mortgage-rates-supply-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20the%20problem%20is%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Elocal%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Where%20homes%20get%20built%2C%20how%20many%2C%20what%20type%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehow%20big%20the%20lot%20has%20to%20be%2C%20how%20many%20meetings%20it%20takes%20to%20build%20something%20new%20%E2%80%94%20those%20things%20are%20all%20governed%20by%20zoning%20rules.%20And%20every%20town%20and%20village%20and%20city%20zones%20itself.%20Which%20means%20there%20are%20more%20than%2030%2C000%20different%20sets%20of%20zoning%20rules%20in%20America.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20housing%2C%20we're%20a%20nation%20of%20islands%2C%20governed%20by%20no%20central%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20each%20of%20those%2030%2C000%20islands%20has%20its%20very%20own%20language%20for%20those%20rules.%20Many%20maps%20favor%20the%20suburban%20ideal%20of%20single-family%20homes%20on%20expansive%20lots%2C%20while%20essentially%20disallowing%20every%20other%20form%20of%20housing.%20One%20place%20might%20call%20a%20two-family%20home%20a%20duplex%20(and%20allow%20it)%2C%20where%20another%20code%20might%20call%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Btownhome%26quot%3B%20or%20just%20%26quot%3Bmultifamily%26quot%3B%20(and%20nix%20it).%20In%20some%20places%2C%20%26quot%3Bmixed-use%26quot%3B%20means%20a%20neighborhood%20that%20combines%20homes%20and%20shops%20(nope!)%3B%20in%20others%20it%20means%20a%20combination%20of%20offices%20and%20industry%20(sure%2C%20why%20not%3F).%20Some%20cities%20have%20maps%20digitally%20coded%20into%20a%20standard%20geospatial%20data%20format%3B%20other%20towns%20still%20use%20paper.%20In%20city%20after%20city%2C%20the%20rules%20are%20woefully%20outdated%2C%20head-scratchingly%20obscure%2C%20or%20outright%20racist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20could%20decipher%20all%20those%20rules%2C%20and%20make%20comparisons%20between%20different%20cities%20and%20states%2C%20you%20might%20be%20able%20to%20figure%20out%20which%20rules%20let%20more%20homes%20get%20built%2C%20and%20which%20ones%20don't.%20But%20no%20one%20has%20ever%20assembled%20America's%20zoning%20regulations%20in%20one%20place%2C%20let%20alone%20force%20them%20to%20use%20the%20same%20words%20to%20mean%20the%20same%20things%20%E2%80%94%20until%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20a%20team%20of%20researchers%20is%20compiling%20every%20city's%20zoning%20rules%20into%20a%20National%20Zoning%20Atlas.%20That%20means%20everyone%20from%20policymakers%20to%20homeowners%20will%20be%20able%20to%20look%20at%20their%20local%20zoning%20maps%20and%20understand%20their%20town's%20hidden%20architecture.%20And%20maybe%2C%20armed%20with%20that%20information%2C%20we'll%20finally%20be%20able%20to%20remodel%20America's%20fixer-upper%20of%20zoning%20policies%20into%20a%20tasteful%20showcase%20for%20starter%20homes%20and%20cheap%20apartments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BZoning%20is%20hugely%20influential%20on%20all%20of%20our%20lives%2C%20and%20people%20don't%20know%20enough%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Sara%20Bronin%2C%20an%20architect%20and%20attorney%20at%20Cornell%20University%20who%20founded%20the%20atlas.%20%26quot%3BOur%20project%20really%20aims%20to%20demystify%20these%20hidden%20rules%2C%20and%20encourage%20policymakers%2C%20researchers%2C%20and%20advocates%20to%20mine%20that%20information.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20atlas%20also%20aims%20to%20translate%20the%20nation's%20multitude%20of%20local%20zoning%20rules%20into%20what%20Bronin%20calls%20a%20%26quot%3Bcommon%20set%20of%20definitions%20and%20practices%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20rationality%20that%20will%20enable%20analysts%2C%20at%20long%20last%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20make%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3Bapples-to-apples%20comparisons.%26quot%3B%20In%20other%20words%2C%20we'll%20finally%20be%20able%20to%20say%2C%20with%20certainty%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdigitalcommons.pepperdine.edu%2Fplr%2Fvol50%2Fiss4%2F2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewhich%20policies%20build%20more%20homes%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20bring%20prices%20down%2C%20and%20which%20policies%20don't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20still%20early%20%E2%80%94%20so%20far%20the%20atlas%20includes%20only%202%2C000%20jurisdictions%20populated%20by%2035%20million%20Americans.%20That's%20because%20it's%20more%20than%20just%20a%20massive%20data%20project%2C%20crunching%20code%20into%20computers.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20legal%20research%20project%2C%26quot%3B%20Bronin%20says%2C%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20biggest%20legal%20research%20projects%20on%20local%20government%20law%20that%20has%20ever%20existed.%20We%20are%20effectively%20reading%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20pages%20of%20local%20ordinances%20and%20regulations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20underestimate%20how%20powerful%20a%20tool%20the%20atlas%20will%20be.%20Bronin%20says%20people%20are%20already%20using%20it%20to%20effect%20policy%20changes%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20woman%20in%20Milford%2C%20Connecticut%2C%20who%20printed%20out%20screenshots%20from%20the%20atlas%20to%20persuade%20her%20town%20to%20change%20its%20policy%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eprohibiting%20residents%20from%20building%20guest-house-type%20units%20in%20their%20backyards.%20Milford's%20official%20zoning%20map%20was%20an%20incomprehensible%20mosaic%20of%20microscale%20neighborhood%20rules%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20the%20easier-to-read%20atlas%20enabled%20the%20Milfordites%20to%20prove%20their%20case%2C%20and%20demand%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%20look%20at%20the%20even%20bigger%20changes%20that%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.planetizen.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F04%2F122638-montana-passes-sweeping-legislative-package-rescind-california-style-zoning%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eenacted%20in%20Montana%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20housing%20prices%20spiked%20sharply%20during%20the%20pandemic%20as%20more%20people%20moved%20to%20Big%20Sky%20Country%20from%20out%20of%20state.%20Armed%20with%20the%20apples-to-apples%20zoning%20maps%20contained%20in%20the%20atlas%2C%20advocates%20for%20zoning%20reform%20were%20able%20to%20compare%20the%20rules%20in%20Montana%20with%20those%20of%20California.%20Cities%20and%20towns%20in%20both%20states%2C%20they%20could%20see%2C%20penalize%20or%20outright%20prohibit%20duplexes%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20housing%20that%20bring%20down%20prices%20and%20help%20prevent%20urban%20sprawl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20able%20to%20come%20into%20legislative%20hearings%20and%20say%3A%20Here's%20a%20map%20of%20Missoula's%20zoning%2C%20here's%20where%20you%20can%20build%20duplexes%2C%20and%20here's%20where%20you%20can't.%20And%20then%20we'd%20put%20a%20map%20next%20to%20it%20of%20Los%20Angeles'%20zoning%2C%20and%20they%20looked%20identical%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Kendall%20Cotton%2C%20a%20prime%20mover%20behind%20the%20push%20for%20zoning%20reform.%20%26quot%3BWe%20said%3A%20Look%2C%20if%20Missoula%20zones%20like%20LA%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20grow%20like%20LA.%20And%20in%2025%20years%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20look%20a%20lot%20like%20LA.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20beauty%20of%20that%20argument%20is%20that%20it%20appealed%20to%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20political%20divide%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20just%20because%20everybody%20came%20together%20over%20their%20shared%20hatred%20of%20Los%20Angeles.%20Enacting%20a%20more%20permissive%20set%20of%20zoning%20rules%20gave%20everyone%20something%20they%20wanted.%20Lefty%20political%20leaders%20knew%20that%20sprawl%20fuels%20climate%20change%20and%20that%20housing%20shortages%20exacerbate%20inequality.%20Right-leaning%20folks%20hoped%20to%20preserve%20their%20right%20to%20build%20whatever%20they%20wanted%20inside%20their%20own%20property%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20put%20it%20on%20a%20map%2C%20it%20was%20undeniable%2C%26quot%3B%20Cotton%20says.%20%26quot%3BThey%20had%20to%20face%20facts%20and%20admit%20that%20what%20their%20zoning%20code%20represents%20is%20not%20conducive%20to%20building%20all%20the%20homes%20they're%20going%20to%20need.%26quot%3B%20Montana%20passed%20new%20rules%20to%20accommodate%20smaller%20multiunit%20buildings%20and%20allow%20duplexes%20anywhere%20single-family%20homes%20are.%20Neighborhoods%20can%20now%20put%20homes%20and%20businesses%20side%20by%20side.%20And%20cities%20now%20have%20to%20meet%20aggressive%20targets%20for%20new%20home%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20atlas%20alone%20won't%20fix%20everything.%20Sometimes%20outdated%2C%20racist%2C%20exclusionary%20zoning%20rules%20exist%20because%20the%20people%20who%20already%20own%20homes%20have%20seen%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-outlook-economy-investors-price-gains-case-shiller-homes-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20their%20values%20skyrocket%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20want%20to%20keep%20things%20the%20way%20they%20are.%20It's%20hard%20to%20imagine%20a%20map%20solving%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLand-use%20policy%20is%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Yonah%20Freemark%2C%20a%20researcher%20at%20the%20Urban%20Institute%20who%20studies%20housing.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20say%20all%20we%20want%20about%20what%20the%20data%20show%2C%20and%20hopefully%20that%20can%20help%20make%20a%20political%20point.%20But%20in%20reality%2C%20this%20requires%20elected%20officials%20and%20community%20groups%20to%20make%20the%20case%20for%20change.%20That's%20a%20political%20question%2C%20not%20a%20data%20question.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFreemark%20thinks%20the%20National%20Zoning%20Atlas%20is%20likely%20to%20make%20more%20of%20a%20difference%20at%20the%20state%20level%20than%20the%20local%20one.%20Yes%2C%20cities%20and%20towns%20make%20their%20own%20zoning%20rules.%20But%20state%20governments%20can%20overrule%20them%2C%20and%20the%20atlas%20may%20arm%20them%20with%20the%20information%20they%20need%20to%20do%20so.%20That%20was%20certainly%20the%20case%20in%20Montana.%20%26quot%3BLocal%20governments%20would%20say%20to%20us%2C%20confidentially%2C%20that%20they%20were%20thankful%2C%20because%20the%20statewide%20legislation%20forces%20their%20hand%2C%26quot%3B%20Cotton%20says.%20%26quot%3BThey%20can%20say%20it's%20the%20legislature's%20fault%3A%20Sorry%2C%20NIMBYs%2C%20now%20we're%20all%20in%20on%20zoning%20reform.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20even%20when%20changes%20are%20implemented%2C%20it%20will%20take%20more%20than%20a%20single%20legislative%20session%20to%20solve%20a%20shortage%20created%20by%20decades%20of%20underbuilding.%20%26quot%3BThe%20state%20of%20California%20has%20been%20passing%20zoning%20change%20after%20zoning%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20Freemark%20says%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20it's%20still%20facing%20low%20housing%20construction%20statewide.%26quot%3B%20But%20we%20have%20to%20start%20somewhere%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20atlas%20offers%20us%20a%20chance%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20the%20housing%20mess%20we've%20created.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20no%20coincidence%20that%20Bronin%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20atlas%2C%20loves%20Italo%20Calvino's%20%26quot%3BInvisible%20Cities.%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20novel%2C%20a%20tale-spinning%20Marco%20Polo%20describes%20to%20Kublai%20Khan%20dozens%20of%20cities%20in%20the%20emperor's%20far-flung%20realm%20that%20may%20or%20may%20not%20exist%2C%20or%20may%20only%20exist%20because%20Polo%20describes%20them.%20That's%20the%20thing%20about%20zoning%3A%20It%20doesn't%20map%20what%20%3Cem%3Eis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(which%20homes%20are%20where)%20but%20what%20%3Cem%3Ecould%20be%20%3C%2Fem%3E(which%20homes%20are%20allowed%20to%20go%20where).%20It's%20a%20map%20of%20the%20future%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20future%20isn't%20fixed.%20There's%20an%20old%20saying%3A%20%3Cem%3EThe%20map%20is%20not%20the%20terrain.%3C%2Fem%3E%20That's%20true.%20But%20the%20right%20map%20can%20change%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fadam-rogers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EAdam%20Rogers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnational-zoning-map-home-prices-down-real-estate-new-houses-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708511221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c526fc43bb77284ba50725%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnational-zoning-map-home-prices-down-real-estate-new-houses-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cities%20and%20states%20are%20using%20the%20National%20Zoning%20Atlas%20to%20understand%20housing%20rules%20and%20bring%20down%20home%20prices.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22arogers%40businessinsider.com%20(Adam%20Rogers)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnational-zoning-map-home-prices-down-real-estate-new-houses-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zimbabwe%20starts%20an%20emergency%20polio%20vaccination%20drive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708510465000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107882143%2Cimgsize-42488.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fzimbabwe-launches-emergency-polio-vaccination-drive-after-detecting-cases-caused-by-rare-mutation%2Farticleshow%2F107882143.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofin