20relief%20under%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20new%20repayment%20reform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Biden%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20the%20Education%20Department%20%E2%80%94%20announced%20that%20153%2C000%20borrowers%20are%20getting%20%241.2%20billion%20in%20debt%20cancellation%20as%20a%20result%20of%20a%20new%20provision%20in%20the%20SAVE%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpecifically%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20announced%20in%20January%20that%20borrowers%20who%20originally%20borrowed%20%2412%2C000%20or%20less%20and%20completed%20as%20few%20as%2010%20years%20of%20qualifying%20payments%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-student-loan-forgiveness-early-income-driven-repayment-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecould%20become%20eligible%20for%20forgiveness%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20change%20from%20the%20prior%20requirement%20of%20at%20least%2020%20years%20of%20qualifying%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20every%20%241%2C000%20a%20borrower%20took%20out%20above%20the%20%2412%2C000%20threshold%2C%20they%20can%20get%20their%20loans%20wiped%20out%20after%20another%20year%20of%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you've%20been%20paying%20for%20a%20decade%2C%20you've%20done%20your%20part%2C%20and%20you%20deserve%20relief%2C%26quot%3B%20Education%20Secretary%20Miguel%20Cardona%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BUnder%20President%20Biden's%20leadership%2C%20our%20Administration%20has%20now%20approved%20loan%20forgiveness%20for%20nearly%203.9%20million%20borrowers%2C%20and%20our%20historic%20fight%20to%20cancel%20student%20debt%20isn't%20over%20yet.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Education%20Department%2C%20Biden%20will%20begin%20sending%20emails%20to%20impacted%20borrowers%20on%20Wednesday%20notifying%20them%20of%20their%20relief%2C%20and%20they%20will%20not%20need%20to%20take%20any%20additional%20action.%20Servicers%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20coming%20days'%26quot%3B%20will%20begin%20applying%20the%20changes%20to%20borrowers'%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoving%20forward%2C%20borrowers%20who%20meet%20the%20eligibility%20criteria%20for%20forgiveness%20under%20the%20SAVE%20Plan%20will%20have%20their%20loans%20automatically%20discharged%20with%20no%20action%20needed%20on%20their%20part%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20press%20release%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20department%20will%20continue%20identifying%20borrowers%20who%20qualify%20for%20relief%20%26quot%3Bon%20a%20regular%20basis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudent-loan%20borrowers%20who%20are%20currently%20not%20on%20the%20SAVE%20plan%20but%20want%20to%20benefit%20from%20this%20shortened%20timeline%20for%20forgiveness%20can%20apply%20to%20enroll%20in%20the%20plan.%20Once%20they%20do%2C%20the%20department%20will%20notify%20them%20of%20any%20relief%20they%20might%20qualify%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Education%20Department%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-debt-borrowers-apply-income-driven-repayment-save-plan-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20implemented%20the%20SAVE%20plan%20over%20the%20summer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20intended%20to%20make%20borrowers'%20monthly%20payments%20cheaper.%20While%20some%20provisions%20of%20the%20plan%20will%20not%20go%20into%20effect%20until%20July%2C%20Wednesday's%20relief%20is%20a%20result%20of%20the%20department%20opting%20for%20early%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20this%20latest%20relief%2C%20the%20department%20has%20also%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-income-driven-repayment-adjustment-debt-relief-biden-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecarrying%20out%20account%20adjustments%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20borrowers%20who%20have%20made%20qualifying%20payments%20under%20income-driven%20repaymeny%20plans%20and%20Public%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%20but%20had%20yet%20to%20receive%20relief.%20Those%20adjustments%20are%20set%20to%20be%20completed%20in%20July%2C%20and%20thousands%20of%20borrowers%20have%20already%20seen%20their%20balances%20wiped%20out%20from%20those%20reforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20relief%20comes%20as%20many%20borrowers%20are%20encountering%20challenges%20with%20the%20return%20to%20repayment%20that%20began%20in%20October.%20Four%20of%20the%20major%20federal%20servicers%20have%20struggled%20to%20manage%20the%20transition%20back%20into%20repayment%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-companies-education-department-punishment-borrowers-repayment-errors-billing-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleaving%20borrowers%20with%20account%20errors%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20timely%20billing%20statements%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Education%20Department%20has%20vowed%20to%20conduct%20oversight%20over%20servicers%2C%20and%20in%20the%20meantime%2C%20it%20is%20continuing%20to%20carry%20out%20targeted%20forms%20of%20relief%20to%20borrowers%20who%20have%20completed%20their%20qualifying%20payments%20on%20repayment%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20too%20long%20the%20system%20did%20not%20work%20for%20borrowers%2C%20even%20when%20they%20were%20eligible%20for%20loan%20forgiveness%2C%26quot%3B%20Under%20Secretary%20of%20Education%20James%20Kvaal%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BToday's%20announcement%20shows%20that%20President%20Biden's%20commitment%20to%20student%20debt%20cancellation%20continues%20to%20deliver.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-debt-cancellation-save-income-driven-payment-plan-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708509661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658300f41c5c7b8c9a0a3d79%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-de