20of%20India%20with%20donation%20details%2C%20including%20donor%20identities%20and%20recipient%20parties%2C%20to%20be%20published%20on%20the%20website%20by%20March%2013%2C%202024.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20court%20has%20suspended%20further%20issuance%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20and%20ordered%20political%20parties%20to%20refund%20un-encashed%20bonds%20within%20the%2015-day%20validity%20period.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20emphasised%20that%20contributions%20made%20to%20influence%20public%20policy%20do%20not%20enjoy%20the%20same%20right%20to%20privacy%20as%20personal%20affiliations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20with%20Vipul%20Mudgal%2C%20director%20of%20Common%20Cause%2C%20a%20petitioner%20in%20the%20said%20case.%20Watch%20the%20interview%20to%20know%20why%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20is%20being%20hailed%20as%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fs3XvT6WrEOw%3Fsi%3DFDOwSdDHX_wfmUer%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708509603000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21132514%2FMudgal-Thumb.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fforeign-powers-could-influence-indian-elections-via-electoral-bonds-vipul-mudgal-on-sc-verdict%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Introduced%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20in%202018%2C%20electoral%20bonds%20allowed%20anonymous%20donations%20from%20companies%20and%20individuals%20to%20political%20parties%2C%20raising%20concerns%20about%20accountability%20and%20potential%20foreign%20interference%20in%20Indian%20elec