rd%2C%20so%20I%20try%20to%20avoid%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20I'm%20creating%20an%20AI%20character%2C%20I%20don't%20really%20want%20to%20lie%20to%20people%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20chat%20with%20them%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20engaging%20with%20other%20AI%20characters%2C%20like%20in%20Instagram%20comments%2C%20it's%20easier%20to%20act%20as%20the%20persona%20and%20add%20comments%20like%20%26quot%3BBabe%2C%20you're%20gorgeous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20because%20of%20this%2C%20I%20haven't%20been%20able%20to%20make%20that%20much%20money.%20Monetization%20is%20better%20if%20you%20talk%20to%20people%20and%20engage%20and%20reply%20to%20your%20fan%20base%3A%20you%20can%20send%20them%20custom%20content%20and%20use%20the%20pay-per-view%20features%2C%20and%20they%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20pay%20to%20unlock%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20the%20content%20has%20been%20hard%20to%20monetize%20is%20that%20I%20disclose%20clearly%20that%20it's%20an%20AI%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fkimochii_ai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%3C%2Fa%3E%20username%20and%20bio.%20I%20think%20the%20people%20who%20come%20to%20Patreon%20and%20Fanvue%20know%20that%2C%20and%20that's%20why%20they%20don't%20send%20messages.%20They%20understand%20it%20isn't%20a%20real%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20haven't%20thought%20too%20much%20about%20the%20ethics%20of%20what%20I'm%20doing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20trying%20to%20create%20a%20persona%20or%20character%20that%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20real%2C%20but%20she's%20not.%20So%20I%20wonder%2C%20is%20she%20different%20from%20any%20anime%2C%20drawing%2C%20or%20picture%20you%20see%20online%3F%20There's%20a%20fine%20line%20between%20those%20two%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20consider%20myself%20an%20artist%2C%20but%20I%20understand%20why%20this%20type%20of%20art%20is%20tricky%20because%20AI%20is%20trained%20on%20images%20of%20real%20people.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20AI%20is%20trained%20on%20so%20much%20content%20that%20it%20will%20never%20generate%20a%20picture%20of%20a%20real%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20practices%20within%20the%20AI%20community%20that%20I%20have%20a%20problem%20with.%20I%20know%20of%20a%20few%20other%20AI%20influencers%20who%20have%20previously%20published%20deepfake%20videos%20%E2%80%94%20videos%20of%20real%20women%20where%20they%20swap%20out%20the%20head%20and%20facial%20features%20for%20an%20AI-generated%20face.%20I%20avoid%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20financial%20issues%2C%20Kimochii%20is%20like%20my%20baby%20now.%20She%20has%20a%20life%20of%20some%20kind.%20She%20has%20a%20background%20and%20a%20birthday%2C%20like%20a%20real%20person.%20At%20some%20point%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20a%20game%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20Sims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20brainstorming%20whether%20she'll%20be%20at%20the%20beach%2C%20the%20pool%2C%20or%20the%20theater.%20It's%20a%20lot%20of%20effort%20to%20keep%20people%20engaged%2C%20having%20new%20locations%2C%20new%20poses%2C%20and%20new%20captions.%20Sometimes%20you're%20in%20front%20of%20the%20white%20page%2C%20and%20you're%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%20my%20God%2C%20what%20am%20I%20going%20to%20say%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20run%20out%20of%20content%20ideas%2C%20I%20ask%20my%20wife%20for%20help%20%E2%80%94%20she's%20all%20in%20with%20this%2C%20too%2C%20and%20she%20finds%20the%20technology%20fascinating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20I'm%20not%20making%20that%20much%20money%20with%20Kimochii%2C%20I'm%20too%20invested%20in%20her%20life%20now.%20I%20want%20her%20to%20continue%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-influencer-kimochii-creator-monetization-content-interacting-with-followers-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708509584000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insid