y%2010%2C%20around%206%20pm%2C%20both%20him%20and%20I%20were%20suspended%20for%20the%20entire%20semester.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20emphasised%20that%20they%20were%20given%20a%20hearing%20notice%20at%2010%3A34%20am%2C%20scheduling%20their%20hearing%20about%20the%20show-cause%20notice%2C%20with%20her%20time%20set%20for%2011%3A30%20am%20and%20his%20for%2011%3A45%20am.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20allotted%20time%20was%20insufficient%20for%20us%20to%20attend%20the%20hearing%20adequately.%20We%20were%20not%20afforded%20enough%20time%20by%20the%20university%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20event%20of%20February%207%2C%20the%20programme%20titled%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Mandir%3A%20A%20Farcical%20Project%20of%20Brahminical%20Hindutva%20Fascism%E2%80%99%20was%20organised%20by%20the%20Revolutionary%20Students%20League%2C%20a%20Marxist%20group%20at%20the%20university.%20Alongside%20the%20two%20in%20question%2C%20eight%20other%20students%20participated%20in%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20friend%20of%20the%20suspended%20student%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20February%207%2C%20this%20discussion%20was%20organised%20on%20the%20university%20campus%20around%208%20pm.%20Approximately%2025%20to%2030%20people%20from%20Abhinav%20Bharat%20%5Ba%20right-wing%20group%5D%20participated%20in%20it.%20As%20this%20programme%20was%20an%20open%20discussion%2C%20any%20student%20could%20participate.%20However%2C%20after%20some%20time%2C%20some%20of%20them%20started%20chanting%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%20while%20others%20recorded%20the%20proceedings.%20In%20response%2C%20the%20RSL%20also%20chanted%20%E2%80%98Inquilab%20Zindabad%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Bheem%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20attempts%20by%20some%20from%20Abhinav%20Bharat%20to%20disrupt%20the%20event%20with%20their%20chants%2C%20the%20RSL%20continued%20with%20their%20discussion.%20They%20further%20alleged%20that%20some%20students%20from%20Abhinav%20Bharat%20recorded%20a%20video%20of%20their%20discussion%2C%20selectively%20edited%20certain%20portions%2C%20and%20circulated%20it%20on%20social%20media.%20Subsequently%2C%20complaints%20were%20lodged%20with%20the%20university%20proctor%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20suspension.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20alleged%20that%20they%20were%20manhandled%20and%20pushed%20out%20of%20the%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2011%2C%20the%20day%20after%20the%20suspension%20on%20February%2010%2C%20both%20students%20were%20forced%20to%20leave%20the%20hostel%20by%20the%20university%20administration%20at%202%20am%2C%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20students%20who%20were%20with%20the%20two%20say%20their%20rooms%20were%20searched%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20were%20allegedly%20denied%20entry%20to%20their%20hostel%20rooms%20at%202%20am%2C%20and%20their%20parents%20called%20at%20that%20time.%20The%20students%20were%20asked%20to%20wait%20in%20the%20parents%E2%80%99%20lounge%20until%20their%20parents%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20this%2C%20one%20of%20the%20students%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%20we%20were%20forced%20and%20thrown%20out%20of%20the%20hostel%20and%20were%20manhandled%20by%20the%20security%20guards.%20Also%2C%20my%20friends%20who%20were%20with%20me%20were%20searched%20in%20the%20room%2C%20which%20is%20completely%20wrong.%20After%20I%20refused%20to%20go%20with%20my%20parents%20at%202%3A30%20am%2C%20I%20was%20forced%20by%20the%20university%20administration%20to%20go%20with%20my%20parents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20February%207%20incident%2C%20both%20suspended%20students%20have%20been%20receiving%20threats%20through%20social%20media%2C%20including%20rape%20and%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20student%20said%20that%20her%20father%20has%20received%20de