rahmanism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20criticism%20of%20the%20character%20and%20actions%20of%20deities%20%E2%80%93%20as%20represented%20in%20the%20scriptures%20%E2%80%93%20is%20what%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20caused%20ire%20among%20Hindutva%20activists.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUndeterred%20by%20the%20threat%2C%20Thakur%20continues%20to%20perform%20across%20the%20state.%20He%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20was%20being%20threatened%20for%20over%20two%20years%20and%20is%20glad%20that%20the%20matter%20is%20no%20longer%20simmering.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20speak%20of%20logic.%20It%20is%20not%20desirable%20to%20have%20obscenity%20in%20the%20scriptures.%20I%20want%20to%20fight%20them%20with%20logic%2C%20not%20with%20force.%20I%20do%20not%20hurt%20anyone%E2%80%99s%20religious%20beliefs.%20Schools%2C%20colleges%20and%20health%20centres%20are%20more%20important%20than%20temple-mosque%20politics.%20Let%20the%20government%20stop%20giving%20sops%20and%20help%20agriculture%20and%20industry%20truly%20flourish.%20Let%20employment%20come%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Thakur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThakur%20added%20that%20he%20is%20not%20likely%20to%20stop.%20%E2%80%9CB.R.%20Ambedkar%2C%20Sri%20Chaitanya%2C%20and%20Harichand%20Guruchand%20Thakur%20have%20said%20worthwhile%20things.%20I%20am%20just%20repeating%20those%20in%20villages%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJayanta%20Bhowmik%2C%20spokesperson%20of%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20is%20one%20who%20does%20not%20see%20this%20kindly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20become%20fashionable%20to%20proclaim%20that%20people%20opposing%20Hinduism%20are%20also%20Hindu.%20Deen%20Krishna%20Thakur%20is%20an%20outcome%20of%20this%20trend.%20Parents%20name%20their%20children%20after%20gods%2C%20so%20it%20is%20disheartening%20if%20the%20child%20later%20adopts%20a%20secular%20stance%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bhowmik.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETraditionally%2C%20kirtan%20songs%20within%20the%20Hindu%20Vaishnava%20community%20have%20served%20as%20devotional%20expressions.%20However%2C%20Thakur%E2%80%99s%20approach%20delves%20deeper%2C%20drawing%20upon%20Hindu%20scriptures%20to%20advocate%20for%20humanism%20over%20rigid%20religious%20structures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20surprised%20that%20radical%20Hinduism%20would%20attack%20a%20folk%20artiste%20like%20this.%20Those%20who%20sing%20kirtan-baul%20songs%20do%20not%20follow%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva%20line.%20Their%20religious%20world%20is%20different.%20But%20these%20attackers%20cannot%20accept%20any%20different%20opinion%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20historian%20Tapati%20Guha-Thakurta%2C%20who%20has%20written%20extensively%20on%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20cultural%20history.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdvocate%20and%20CPI(M)%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Bikash%20Ranjan%20Bhattacharya%20said%20that%20an%20attack%20on%20an%20artiste%20is%20never%20acceptable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Bengal%20rights%20groups%20have%20voiced%20their%20support%20for%20Thakur%2C%20the%20music%20fraternity%20has%20remained%20conspicuously%20quiet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708506051000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165202%2FUntitled-design-2-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fkirtan-deen-krishna-thakur-hindutva-attack%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Traditionally%2C%20kirtan%20songs%20served%20as%20devotional%20expressions.%20However%2C%20Deen%20Krishna%20Thakur's%20advocated%20for%20humanism%20over%20rigid%20religious%20structures.%C2%A0This%20angered%20local%20Hindutva%20groups.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fkirtan-deen-krishna-thakur-