ons%20in%202024.%20It's%20not%20being%20called%20a%20mega-election%20year%20for%20nothing-over%2050%20countries%20worldwide%20and%20half%20the%20world's%20population%20is%20voting%20in%20national%20elections%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20that%20has%20emerged%20today%20is%20Generative%20Artificial%20Intelligence(AI)-induced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fexclusive%2Fnews%2Fdeepfakes-equivalent-to-misinformation-rajeev-chandrasekhar-tells-ndtv-741028%5C%22%3Emis-%20and%20disinformation.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Risk%20from%20it%20has%20been%20rated%20as%20the%20most%20pressing%20issue%20in%20the%20short%20term%20by%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum's%20Global%20Risk%20Report%202024.%20It%20surpasses%20even%20climate%20change%2C%20war%2C%20and%20economic%20weakness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20over%2035%20experts%20from%20the%20European%20Union%20(EU)%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Freporter-vlogs%2Findia-needs-dedicated-law-to-punish-creators-of-deepfakes-cyber-law-expert-pawan-duggal-741348%5C%22%3EIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20coming%20together%20in%20New%20Delhi%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-come-up-with-regulation-penalty-likely-for-creating-deepfakes-and-platforms-hosting-them-4598838%5C%22%3Elook%20at%20ways%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20tackle%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fthe-last-word%2Ftackling-deepfakes-regulations-penalties-in-offing-amid-rising-concerns-740901%5C%22%3Ethreat%20of%20online%20disinformation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20information%20manipulation.%20The%20Deputy%20Head%20of%20the%20Delegation%20of%20the%20European%20Union%20to%20India%2C%20Seppo%20Nurmi%2C%20has%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20physical%20world%2C%20Europe%20might%20seem%20far%20away%20from%20Asia%2C%20but%20in%20cyberspace%2C%20we%20live%20together%2C%20sometimes%20in%20a%20complex%2C%20dangerous%20cyber-neighbourhood%20where%20our%20societies%20depend%20on%20resilient%2C%20trustworthy%20digital%20services%2C%20and%20where%20we%20can%20all%20become%20victim%20to%20malicious%20cyber-attacks.%20We%20need%20to%20combat%20such%20challenges%20with%20mutual%20defence%20and%20strong%2C%20trusted%20cooperation.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETechnology%20is%20not%20bound%20by%20borders%2C%20and%20that%20makes%20it%20critical%20for%20all%20stakeholders%20to%20work%20collectively.%20While%20countries%20all%20across%20the%20world%20grapple%20with%20the%20threat%20of%20Generative%20AI%20to%20elections%20and%20democracies%2C%20the%20response%20to%20the%20challenge%20is%20being%20conducted%20largely%20in%20silos%20-%20separate%20governments%20formulating%20laws%2C%20private%20software%20companies%20coming%20out%20with%20guidelines%2C%20with%20the%20UN%20Secretary-General%20also%20expressing%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EFrom%20Bangladesh%20To%20US%20-%20Worrying%20Trends%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20perils%20of%20AI%20are%20already%20visible%20in%20elections%20the%20world%20over.%20Bangladesh%20polls%20saw%20worrying%20developments%2C%20with%20deepfakes%20targeting%20some%20non-ruling%20party%20candidates%20and%20leaders.%20Two%20independent%20candidates%20were%20seen%20announcing%20their%20withdrawal%20from%20the%20polls%2C%20but%20it%20turned%20out%20that%20both%20videos%20were%20digitally%20manipulated%20using%20deep%20generative%20methods.%20And%20in%20what%20was%20later%20revealed%20to%20be%20a%20deepfake%2C%20opposition%20leader%20Tarique%20Rahman%20was%20seen%20urging%20people%20not%20to%20be%20critical%20of%20Israel%20for%20bombing%20Gaza%2C%20a%20position%20that%20is%20politically%20fatal%20in%20Muslim-majority%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndonesia's%20president%20elect%2C%20Prabowo%20Subianto%2C%20was%20projected%20as%20an%20adorable%2C%20cuddly%20character%20via%20generative%20AI%2C%20creating%20an%20image%20far%20removed%20from%20his%20fiery%20military%20character.%20The%20technologically%20created%20image%20appealed%20to%20the%20youth%20voter%2C%20leading%20to%20Subianto's%20victory%2C%20though%20official%20results%20will%20be%20announced%20in%20March.%20The%20former%20army%20general%20has%20been%20accused%20in%20the%20past%20of%20human%20rights%20violations%20and%20was%20also%20banned%20from%20travelling%20to%20countries%20like%20the%20US.%20Many%20wonder%20what%20his%20rise%20to%20power%20will%20mean%20for%20democracy%20in%20Indonesia.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20a%20campaign%20ad%20by%20the%20Republican%20Party%20in%20the%20US%20showed%20a%20dystopian%3Cbr%3E%5Cnfuture%20if%20Joe%20Biden%20is%20re-elected%20President.%20These%20images%20were%20also%20created%20using%20generative%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat%20Are%20Deepfakes%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrade%20association%20techUK%20describes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fleft-right-centre%2Fwhat-are-deepfakes-and-how-you-can-spot-them-740400%5C%22%3Edeepfakes%20%3C%2Fa%3Eas%20synthetic%20media%20that%20focus%20on%20manipulating%20or%20altering%20visual%20or%20auditory%20information%2C%20to%20create%20convincing%20fake%20content%2C%20ranging%20from%20images%2C%20audio%20and%20video.%20It%20also%20says%20they%20serve%20as%20amplifiers%20of%20existing%20threats%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Bdeceptive%20campaign%20ads%2C%20mis-%20and%20disinformation%2C%20voter%20suppression%2C%20and%20attacks%20on%20election%20workers%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20Common%20Watchdog%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UNESCO%20suggested%20a%20set%20of%20guidelines%20in%202021%20for%20the%20responsible%20use%20of%20AI%20-%20Recommendations%20on%20the%20Ethics%20of%20Artificial%20Intelligence.%20However%2C%20this%20largely%20works%20within%20the%20UNESCO%20mandate%20on%20education%2C%20science%20and%20culture.%20In%20further%20efforts%2C%20tech%20companies%20like%20Adobe%2C%20Arm%2C%20BBC%2C%20Intel%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20Truepic%20came%20up%20with%20some%20technical%20standards%20that%20provide%20publishers%2C%20creators%2C%20and%20consumers%20the%20ability%20to%20trace%20the%20origin%20of%20different%20types%20of%20media.%20And%20while%20the%20EU%20has%20also%20passed%20new%20regulations%20for%20AI%2C%20which%20include%20provisions%20for%20transparency%20and%20accountability%20in%20AI%20systems%2C%20the%20US%20has%20passed%20the%20National%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20Initiative%20Act%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20promote%20the%20development%20and%20responsible%20use%20of%20AI.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20need%20of%20the%20hour%20is%20for%20such%20efforts%20to%20be%20combined%20and%20have%20an%20overarching%20agency%20like%20the%20UN%20take%20charge%2C%20since%20AI%20can%20pose%20a%20danger%20to%20global%20stability.%20Weakened%20democracies%2C%20lack%20of%20confidence%20in%20elected%20governments%20or%20governments%20lacking%20legitimacy%20can%20lead%20to%20instability%20within%20countries%20and%20mistrust%20between%20countries%2C%20possibly%20leading%20to%20further%20conflicts.%20The%20matter%20should%20perhaps%20be%20dealt%20with%20the%20same%20urgency%20as%20shown%20in%20tackling%20climate%20change%20under%20the%20UNFCCC%20(United%20Nations%20Framework%20Convention%20on%20Climate%20Change).%20Collective%20action%20is%20required%20to%20ensure%20generative%20AI%20doesn't%20turn%20into%20an%20uncontrolled%20behemoth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Maha%20Siddiqui%20is%20a%20journalist%20who%20has%20extensively%20reported%20on%20public%20policy%20and%20global%20affairs.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708504260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F295nvsms_deepfake-generic_625x300_22_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fai-elections-and-law-india-eu-talks-underline-why-collective-action-is-important-5099192%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Talks%20between%20EU%20and%20India%20on%20tackling%20the%20threat%20of%20online%20disinformation%20reflect%20the%20need%20for%20collective%20global%20action%20against%20the%20risks%20posed%20by%20generative%20AI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fai-elections-and-law-india-eu-talks-underline-why-collective-action-is-important-5099192%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fai-elections-and-law-india-eu-talks-underline-why-collective-action-is-important-5099192%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fai-elections-and-law-india-eu-talks-underline-why-collective-action-is-important-5099192%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Escape%20Route%2C%20Alarm%20Systems%20Absent%20in%20Silkyara%20Tunnel%20in%20Uttarakhand%3A%20Expert%20Panel%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01140335%2FGACaXNpbYAASMBx.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20the%20aftermath%20of%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Silkyara%20tunnel%20collapse%20where%2041%20workers%20were%20trapped%20for%2017%20days%20in%20November%2C%20an%20expert%20panel%20constituted%20to%20probe%20the%20incident%20underlined%20that%20there%20was%20an%20absence%20of%20an%20escape%20route%20and%20alarm%20systems%20in%20the%20structure%20and%20pointed%20out%20other%20shortcomings%20in%20the%20planning%20and%20designing%20of%20the%20tunnel%2C%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fmonths-after-uttarakhand-tunnel-collapse-panel-flags-shortcomings-in-planning-101708424967605.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20no%20escape%20route%20and%20an%20alarm%20system%20in%20case%20of%20tragedy.%20Even%20monitoring%20was%20not%20proper%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shantanu%20Sarkar%2C%20director%20of%20Uttarakhand%20Landslide%20Mitigation%20and%20Management%20Centre%2C%20who%20led%20the%20six-member%20expert%20committee%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20underlined%20that%20the%20design%20report%20%E2%80%9Clacked%20detailed%20geotechnical%20and%20geophysical%20investigations%E2%80%9D.%20Further%2C%20the%2070-page%20report%20called%20for%20a%20detailed%20safety%20audit%20of%20the%20tunnel%2C%20adding%20that%20safety%20should%20never%20be%20compromised%20to%20meet%20completion%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConducting%20more%20exploratory%20bore-holes%20and%20geophysical%20investigations%20can%20identify%20critical%20geological%20features%20and%20minimise%20risks%20during%20construction%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20mentioned%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForty-one%20workers%20were%20trapped%20for%2017%20days%20in%20the%20collapsed%20Silkyara%20tunnel%20in%20Uttarkashi%20after%20it%20collapsed.%20They%20were%20pulled%20out%20after%20manual%20digging%20for%20over%2026%20hours%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20primitive%20rat-hole%20mining%20method.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20key%20highlights%20of%20the%20report%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-google-query-id%3D%5C%22CPGmhKLdu4QDFVmKZgIdduUMwA%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CManual%20monitoring%2C%20conducted%20periodically%2C%20may%20not%20provide%20timely%20insights%20into%20evolving%20situations.%20Shifting%20towards%20real-time%20monitoring%20can%20offer%20proactive%20responses%20to%20dynamic%20conditions%20within%20the%20tunnel%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20mentioned%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CImplementing%20an%20evacuation%20plan%2C%20such%20as%20installing%20concrete%20hume%20pipes%2C%20is%20essential%20to%20facilitate%20quick%20evacuation%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20collapse%20tragedy.%20Incorporating%20an%20alarm%20system%20for%20evacuation%20is%20essential%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20works%E2%80%A6.%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20panel%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcollapses-during-silkyara-tunnel-construction-central-team%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9919-20%E2%80%B2%20Collapses%20During%20Silkyara%20Tunnel%20Construction%20in%20Last%205%20Years%3A%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERecommendations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20panel%2C%20for%20a%20Silkyara-like%C2%A0project%20in%20the%20future%20comprehensive%20site%20study%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20assessing%20rock%20formations%2C%20seismic%20activity%2C%20and%20potential%20risks%20to%20ensure%20that%20tunnels%20are%20designed%20to%20withstand%20the%20geological%20challenges%20of%20the%20region%20%E2%80%93%20is%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20report%20recommended%20formulation%20of%20project-specific%20Standard%20Operating%20Procedures%20and%20proper%20training%20for%20workers.%C2%A0For%20tunnel%20collapses%2C%20the%20panel%20suggested%20that%20detailed%20and%20scenario-specific%20emergency%20plans%20should%20be%20formulated.%20It%20also%20underlined%20that%20design%20engineers%20should%20conduct%20regular%20inspections%20to%20identify%20%E2%80%9Cdeviations%20and%20implement%20corrective%20measures%20to%20deal%20with%20geological%20surprises%E2%80%9D%20and%20technical%20advisory%20committee%20should%20also%20be%20constituted%20to%20visit%20the%20tunnel%20at%20regular%20intervals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20regularly%20monitor%20similar%20projects%20in%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20the%20panel%20suggested%20an%20interdepartmental%20coordination%20committee%20to%20be%20constituted%20at%20the%20national%2C%20state%2C