ased%20bias%20are%20constitutionally%20impermissible.%20Rules%20making%20marriage%20of%20women%20employees%20and%20their%20domestic%20involvement%20a%20ground%20for%20disentitlement%20would%20be%20unconstitutional%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said%20in%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20however%2C%20modified%20the%20tribunal's%20ruling%20to%20reinstate%20the%20employee%20and%20provide%20back%20wages.%20Instead%2C%20it%20asked%20the%20Centre%20to%20pay%20Rs%2060%20lakh%20in%20compensation.%20The%20bench%20also%20noted%20that%20LJohn%20had%20worked%20as%20a%20nurse%20in%20a%20private%20organisation%20for%20a%20short%20time.%20The%20court%20said%20the%20payment%20of%20compensation%20must%20be%20made%20within%20eight%20weeks%20of%20the%20Centre%20receiving%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708502400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fcq5c2cmg_supreme-court-reuters_625x300_06_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-patriarchal-top-court-rules-in-favour-of-army-nurse-fired-over-marriage-5098841%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Terminating%20a%20woman's%20employment%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20marriage%20was%20%26quot%3Bcoarse%20case%20of%20gender%20discrimination%26quot%3B%20and%20any%20law%20based%20on%20a%20gender%20bias%20is%20%26quot%3Bconstitutionally%20impermissible%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20said%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-patriarchal-top-court-rules-in-favour-of-army-nurse-fired-over-marriage-5098841%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-patriarchal-top-court-rules-in-favour-of-army-nurse-fired-over-marriage-5098841%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-patriarchal-top-court-rules-in-favour-of-army-nur