sian-ballerina-ksenia-karelina-detained-accused-of-supporting-ukraine-after-51-donation-5098811%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famerican-russian-ballerina-ksenia-karelina-detained-accused-of-supporting-ukraine-after-51-donation-5098811%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNever%20My%20Intention...%26quot%3B%3A%20Vikrant%20Apologises%20For%20Old%20Lord%20Ram-Sita%20Cartoon%20Tweet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EActor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsearch%3Fsearchtext%3DVikrant-Massey-%5C%22%3EVikrant%20Massey%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20found%20himself%20in%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20controversy%20after%20an%20old%20tweet%20shared%20by%20the%20actor%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20once%20again.%20The%202018%20tweet%2C%20made%20in%20connection%20to%20the%20gangrape%20and%20murder%20of%20an%20eight-year-old%20girl%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20also%20included%20a%20cartoon%20featuring%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20Goddess%20Sita.%20This%20has%20led%20to%C2%A0fresh%C2%A0outrage%20among%20social%20media%20users.%20Apologising%20for%20the%20same%2C%C2%A0Vikrant%20Massey%2C%20on%20Wednesday%2C%C2%A0said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20context%20to%20one%20of%20my%20Tweets%20way%20back%20in%202018%2C%20I'd%20like%20to%20say%20a%20few%20words%3A%20It%20was%20never%20my%20intention%20to%20hurt%2C%20malign%20or%20disrespect%20the%20Hindu%20community.%20But%20as%20I%20reflect%20in%20hindsight%20about%20a%20Tweet%20made%20in%20jest%2C%20I%20also%20release%20the%20distasteful%20nature%20of%20it.%20The%20same%20could%20have%20been%20said%20without%20adding%20the%20cartoon%20which%20was%20published%20in%20a%20newspaper.%C2%A0%20And%20I'd%20with%20utmost%20humility%20like%20to%20apologise%20to%20each%20and%20everyone%20who%20has%20been%20hurt.%20As%20you%20all%20by%20now%20know%2C%20that%20I%20hold%20all%20faiths%2C%20beliefs%20and%20religions%20with%20the%20highest%20possible%20regard.%C2%A0%20We%20all%20grow%20up%20with%20time%20and%20reflect%20upon%20our%20mistakes.%20This%20was%20mine.%20Regards%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIn%20context%20to%20one%20of%20my%20Tweets%20way%20back%20in%202018%2C%20I'd%20like%20to%20say%20a%20few%20words%3A%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt%20was%20never%20my%20intention%20to%20hurt%2C%20malign%20or%20disrespect%20the%20Hindu%20community.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnBut%20as%20I%20reflect%20in%20hindsight%20about%20a%20Tweet%20made%20in%20jest%2C%20I%20also%20release%20the%20distasteful%20nature%20of%20it.%20The%20same%20could%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Vikrant%20Massey%20(%40VikrantMassey)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVikrantMassey%2Fstatus%2F1760015732581204116%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2020%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202018%20tweet%20by%20Vikrant%20Massey%20included%20an%20editorial%20cartoon%20which%20featured%20Goddess%20Sita%20telling%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20%E2%80%9CI'm%20so%20glad%20I%20was%20kidnapped%20by%20Ravan%20and%20not%20by%20your%20bhakts!%E2%80%9D%20%C2%A0Along%20with%20the%20cartoon%2C%20Vikrant%20Massey%20had%20written%20on%20X%20%5Bformerly%20Twitter%5D%3A%20%E2%80%9CHalf-baked%20potatoes%20and%20half-baked%20nationalists%20will%20only%20cause%20a%20pain%20in%20the%20gut.%20%23KathuaCase%C2%A0%23Unnao%20%23Shame.%E2%80%9D%20The%20tweet%2C%20which%20once%20again%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20has%20since%20been%20deleted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20comes%20just%20days%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fvikrant-massey-on-brother-moeen-s-religion-conversion-5093922%5C%22%3EVikrant%20Massey%2C%20in%20an%20interview%2C%20shared%20that%20he%20grew%20up%20in%20an%20inclusive%20household%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhere%20his%20family%20members%20follow%20varied%20religions.%20On%20the%20show%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20hr