properly%20vet%20its%20customers%2C%20ensnaring%20top%20lenders%20from%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20to%20Citigroup%20Inc.%20Fed%20up%20with%20the%20persistent%20shortcomings%2C%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20is%20likely%20to%20get%20even%20tougher%20before%20Governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20steps%20down%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRBI%20has%20enough%20tools%20and%20a%20penalty%20is%20just%20the%20beginning%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Prakash%20Agarwal%2C%20founder%20of%20Gefion%20Capital%20Advisors.%20He%20said%20the%20fines%20serve%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsymbolic%20warning%20for%20more%20dire%20measures%20to%20come%2C%20such%20as%20a%20sledgehammer%20action%20taken%20against%20Paytm%20bank.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegulatory%20concerns%20are%20rising%20as%20lenders%20rush%20to%20open%20more%20accounts%20and%20mop%20up%20deposits%20to%20meet%20the%20soaring%20demand%20for%20loans%20in%20the%20fastest-growing%20major%20economy.%20Most%20banks%20typically%20outsource%20the%20last%20mile%20of%20customer%20verification%20to%20third-party%20firms%20or%20so-called%20runners%2C%20and%20leakages%20occur%20at%20many%20points%20in%20that%20largely%20paper%20process%2C%20according%20to%20Ashok%20Hariharan%2C%20chief%20executive%20officer%20of%20IDfy%2C%20which%20provides%20client%20vetting%20services%20to%20banks%20and%20fintechs%20firms%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20big%20banks%20can%20do%20more%2C%20it's%20a%20challenge%20dealing%20with%20firms%20that%20don't%20have%20strict%20fraud%20and%20risk%20teams%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERBI%20Governor%20Das%20has%20repeatedly%20warned%20about%20the%20need%20to%20strengthen%20risk%20management%20in%20banks%20and%20shadow%20lenders.%20Even%20though%20bad%20debts%20are%20at%20a%20more%20than%20decade%20low%2C%20these%20lapses%20in%20customer%20verification%20have%20been%20among%20major%20concerns%20for%20the%20central%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20interest%20of%20depositors%20and%20customers%20is%20of%20prime%20importance%2C%26quot%3B%20Das%20said%20in%20a%20post-monetary%20policy%20briefing%20this%20month.%20%26quot%3BFinancial%20stability%20is%20of%20prime%20importance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Indian%20banks%20have%20boosted%20spending%20on%20technology%20to%20detect%20potential%20money%20laundering%20and%20prevent%20fraud%2C%20the%20cases%20are%20rising.%20The%20number%20of%20reported%20frauds%20of%20more%20than%20100%2C000%20rupees%20(%241%2C205)%20rose%2068%25%20to%20more%20than%2014%2C000%20from%20April%20to%20September%20last%20year%2C%20almost%20triple%20the%20rate%20for%20the%20previous%20six-month%20period%2C%20according%20to%20an%20RBI%20report.%20The%20sharpest%20increase%20of%20fraud%20cases%20was%20in%20credit%20cards%2C%20online%20transactions%20and%20deposits%2C%20the%20data%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERBI%2C%20which%20can%20levy%20a%20maximum%20penalty%20of%2050%20million%20rupees%20for%20violations%2C%20imposed%20fines%20of%20400%20million%20rupees%20in%20the%20fiscal%20year%20that%20ended%20in%20March%2C%20down%20from%20650.3%20million%20rupees%20the%20prior%20year.%20Still%2C%20in%20the%20current%20fiscal%20year%2C%20the%20frequency%20of%20such%20fines%20has%20increased%20sharply%2C%20as%20can%20be%20parsed%20from%20the%20central%20bank's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRBI%20getting%20stricter%20on%20KYC%20is%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do%2C%20and%20people%20are%20going%20to%20get%20serious%20about%20it%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20IDfy's%20Hariharan.%20%26quot%3BIn%20many%20instances%2C%20there%20is%20a%20frivolous%20attitude%20toward%20KYC.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECustomer%20data%20in%20the%20country%20has%20been%20misused%2C%20according%20to%20Hariharan.%20In%20a%20typical%20set-up%2C%20fraudsters%20pay%20runners%20who%20collect%20so-called%20Know-Your-Customer%20documents%20for%20bank%20customers%20and%20offer%20them%20as%20little%20as%20500%20rupees%20for%20the%20data%2C%20he%20said.%20This%20allows%20fraudsters%20to%20operate%20multiple%20bank%20accounts%20from%20the%20identity%20theft%2C%20and%20they%20collect%20money%20in%20these%20accounts%20by%20duping%20customers%20largely%20through%20phishing%20calls%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECrackdown%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20its%20crackdown%20on%20banks%2C%20RBI%20ordered%20Visa%20Inc.%20this%20month%20to%20immediately%20stop%20a%20payments%20service%20where%20cards%20were%20used%20to%20transact%20with%20merchants%20who%20weren't%20allowed%20to%20accept%20such%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20no%20recent%20case%20has%20drawn%20as%20much%20attention%20as%20Paytm%2C%20controlled%20by%20billionaire%20Vijay%20Shekhar%20Sharma.%20The%20firm%20burst%20onto%20India's%20equity%20markets%20in%202021%20with%20a%20%242.5%20billion%20initial%20public%20offering%2C%20the%20largest%20ever%20in%20the%20country%20and%20attracted%20a%20who's%20who%20of%20global%20investors.%20Masayoshi%20Son's%20SoftBank%20was%20on%20board%2C%20as%20was%20China%20fintech%20giant%20Ant%20Group%20Co.%20and%20the%20Canada%20Pension%20Plan%20Investment%20Board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20affiliate%20company%2C%20which%20takes%20deposits%20and%20offers%20payment%20services%20much%20like%20PayPal%20Holdings%20Inc.%2C%20has%20been%20in%20the%20regulator's%20crosshairs.%20On%20January%2031%2C%20RBI%20barred%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20Ltd.%20from%20accepting%20fresh%20credits%20in%20its%20customer%20accounts%20or%20mobile%20wallets%20after%20February%2029.%20Bloomberg%20News%20has%20reported%20that%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20customers%20didn't%20submit%20their%20KYC%20documentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20move%20dealt%20a%20big%20blow%20to%20Paytm%20and%20sent%20its%20stock%20tumbling.%20Regulators%20last%20week%20extended%20that%20deadline%20to%20March%2015%2C%20and%20Paytm%20is%20in%20talks%20with%20other%20banks%20to%20clear%20merchant%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompliance%20and%20accountability%20are%20big%20challenges%20for%20the%20financial%20system%2C%20which%20now%20includes%20a%20lot%20of%20links%20among%20banks%2C%20fintechs%20and%20others%2C%20according%20to%20K.V.%20Karthik%2C%20who%20leads%20the%20financial%20services%20sector%20for%20Deloitte%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20such%20a%20sharp%20growth%20in%20so%20many%20small%20fintech%20firms%20in%20the%20ecosystem%2C%20RBI%20probably%20wants%20to%20put%20out%20a%20stern%20and%20clear%20message%20that%20everyone%20must%20follow%20rules%20very%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gefion%20Capital's%20Agarwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708501200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fmiln3j4k_vijay-shekhar-sharma-bloomberg_625x300_21_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fvijay-shekhar-sharma-rbi-clampdown-on-embattled-fintech-star-paytm-sparks-industry-concerns-5098934%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20regulators%20seeking%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20potential%20fraud%20in%20the%20financial%20sector%2C%20Paytm%20may%20just%20be%20the%20beginning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fvijay-shekhar-sharma-rbi-clampdown-on-embattled-fintech-star-paytm-sparks-industry-concerns-5098934%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fvijay-shekhar-sharma-rbi-clampdown-on-embattled-fintech-star-paytm-sparks-industry-concerns-5098934%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fvijay-shekhar-sharma-rbi-clampdown-on-embattled-fintech-star-paytm-sparks-industry-concerns-5098934%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Not%20Joined%20INDIA%20Bloc%2C%20Will%20Support%20Anyone%20Who...%3A%20Kamal%20Haasan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EActor-politician%20Kamal%20Haasan%20today%20said%20discussions%20were%20on%20for%20his%20party%20MNM's%20political%20alliance%20and%20stressed%20it%20would%20support%20any%20bloc%20that%20would%20%26quot%3Bselflessly%26quot%3B%20think%20about%20the%20nation%20but%20desist%20from%20being%20part%20of%20%26quot%3Bfeudal%20politics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20reporters%20here%20after%20leading%20the%207th%20anniversary%20celebrations%20of%20his%20Makkal%20Needhi%20Maiam%2C%20Mr%20Haasan%20also%20welcomed%20the%20recent%20political%20entry%20of%20top%20Tamil%20actor%20Vijay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20MNM%20will%20join%20the%20multi-party%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20already%20told%2C%20this%20is%20the%20time%20when%20you%20have%20to%20blur%20party%20politics%20and%20think%20about%20the%20nation.%20Anybody%20who%20thinks%20selflessly%20about%20the%20nation%2C%20my%20MNM%20will%20be%20part%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20MNM%20won't%20join%20hands%20with%20those%20doing%20%26quot%3Blocal%20feudal%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20he%20has%20joined%20the%20INDIA%20grouping%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bno%2C%20I%20haven't.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20party's%20possible%20political%20alliance%2C%20he%20said%20%26quot%3Bdiscussions%20are%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20any%20%26quot%3Bgood%20news%26quot%3B%20in%20this%20regard%20will%20be%20communicated%20to%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20was%20asked%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20speculations%20that%20Haasan's%20party%20was%20involved%20in%20alliance%20talks%20with%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin-led%20DMK%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMNM%20had%20earlier%20faced%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20the%202021%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Assembly%20elections%20but%20failed%20to%20put%20up%20an%20impressive%20show.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708500780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F295t176s_kamal-haasan-ani_625x300_21_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-joined-india-bloc-will-support-anyone-who-kamal-haasan-5098790%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Actor-politician%20Kamal%20Haasan%20today%20said%20discussions%20were%20on%20for%20his%20party%20MNM's%20political%20alliance%20and%20stressed%20it%20would%20support%20any%20bloc%20that%20would%20%26quot%3Bselflessly%26quot%3B%20think%20about%20the%20nation%20but%20desist%20from%20being%20part%20of%20%26quot%3Bfeudal%20politics.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-joined-india-bloc-will-support-anyone-who-kamal-haasan-5098790%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-joined-india-bloc-will-support-anyone-who-kamal-haasan-5098790%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-joined-india-bloc-will-support-anyone-who-kamal-haasan-5098790%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20Delegation%20Meets%20'One%20Nation%20One%20Election'%20Panel%2C%20Backs%20Proposal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21123414%2FUntitled-design-11.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20on%20Monday%2C%20February%2020%2C%20told%20the%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%20committee%2C%20chaired%20by%20former%20president%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%2C%20to%20synchronise%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20state%20assembly%20elections%20at%20least%20to%20begin%20with%20before%20local%20body%20polls%20are%20also%20clubbed%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELed%20by%20party%20chief%20J.P.%20Nadda%2C%20a%20four-member%20delegation%20of%20the%20party%20called%20on%20the%20Kovind%20panel%20and%20submitted%20a%20written%20memorandum%20favouring%20simultaneous%20polls.%20The%20party%20said%20multiple%20elections%20and%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20affect%20the%20delivery%20of%20good%20governance%2C%20affecting%20the%20development%20of%20the%20country.%20It%20also%20said%20a%20lot%20of%20wasteful%20expenditure%20can%20be%20saved%20by%20holding%20elections%20across%20the%20country%20at%20once.%20The%20party%20said%20multiple%20polls%20lead%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20financial%20burden%20on%20the%20parties%20as%20well%20and%20this%20becomes%20a%20reason%20for%20corruption.%20Security%20forces%20that%20are%20deployed%20for%20internal%20and%20external%20security%20on%20the%20border%20are%20and%20again%20deployed%20in%20the%20states%20for%20the%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nadda%20told%20the%20media%20after%20meeting%20the%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20requested%20that%20there%20should%20be%20one%20photo%20identity%20card%20which%20is%20valid%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20State%20Assembly%20and%20panchayat%20polls.%20There%20should%20be%20one%20voter%20list%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20State%20Assembly%20and%20panchayat.%20If%20it%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20done%20immediately%2C%20then%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Assemblies%20should%20be%20done%20together%20and%20later%20think%20of%20the%20panchayat%20(polls).%20But%20all%20panchayat%20elections%20should%20be%20together%2C%20otherwise%20the%20MCC%20will%20be%20in%20force%20repeatedly.%20In%20the%20long%20run%2C%20the%20three%20elections%20should%20be%20together%2C%20and%20for%20that%20there%20should%20be%20consensus%2C%20amendment%20to%20the%20RP%20Act%20and%20the%20activities%20to%20be%20taken%20up%20after%20delimitation%20should%20be%20done%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nadda%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20among%20four%20political%20parties%20that%20have%20supported%20the%20idea.%20The%20others%20being%20All%20India%20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(AIADMK)%2C%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%2C%20and%20Maharashtrawadi%20Gomantak%20Party%C2%A0%20(MGP).%20However%2C%20at%20least%20eight%20opposition%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%2C%20opposed%20the%20idea%2C%20stating%20that%20such%20an%20idea%20would%20hurt%20India%E2%80%99s%20federalism%20and%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%20figured%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20election%20manifestos%20of%202014%20and%202019.%20The%202019%20manifesto%20had%20said%20the%20party%20would%20work%20to%20%E2%80%9Cbuild%20consensus%20on%20this%20issue%20with%20all%20parties%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kovind%20panel%20was%20established%20by%20the%20Union%20law%20ministry%20on%20September%202%20last%20year%20to%20suggest%20ways%20to%20hold%20elections%20simultaneously.%20As%20a%20part%20of%20its%20consultations%2C%20the%20committee%20had%20in%20October%20written%20to%20national%20and%20state%20parties%20seeking%20their%20views%20on%20simultaneous%20elections.%20Since%20then%2C%20it%20has%20been%20meeting%20political%20parties%20to%20discuss%20their%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708500596000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21123414%2FUntitled-design-11.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-delegation-meets-one-nation-one-election-panel-backs-proposal%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Led%20by%20party%20president%20J.P.%20Nadda%2C%20a%20four-member%20delegation%20told%20the%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20panel%20that%20multiple%20elections%20affect%20good%20governance%20and%20development%20as%20well%20as%20result%20in%20corruption.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-delegation-meets-one-nation-one-election-panel-backs-proposal%22%2C%22cd