20area%20of%20north%20Kashmir%20on%20February%2017%20during%20which%20a%20forest%20official%20identified%20as%20Bashir%20Ahmad%20Dobhi%20was%20found%20wearing%20a%20pheran%2C%20a%20traditional%2C%20cloak-type%20garment%20used%20by%20Kashmiris%20to%20keep%20themselves%20warm%20in%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%2C%20who%20was%20recently%20posted%20in%20Langate%2C%20later%20set%20up%20a%20departmental%20inquiry%20against%20Dobhi%2C%20a%20forest%20guard%2C%20while%20placing%20him%20under%20suspension%20for%20%E2%80%9Clooking%20like%20a%20shepherd%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20territorial%20forest%20officials%20are%20part%20of%20a%20disciplined%20force%20and%20are%20always%20duty%20bound%20to%20wear%20proper%20dress%20code%20while%20performing%20their%20duties%20at%20sensitive%20postings%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20suspension%20order%20issued%20by%20Pajwari%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20is%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Range%20Officer%20Mawar%20shall%20make%20an%20internal%20arrangements%20in%20place%20of%20the%20suspended%20official%20till%20suitable%20staff%20is%20posted%20in%20the%20said%20check-post%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20order%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9Cshepherd%E2%80%9D%20in%20an%20allegedly%20derogatory%20and%20racist%20manner%20by%20the%20senior%20officer%20triggered%20outrage%20in%20Kashmir.%20Amid%20snowfall%2C%20a%20group%20of%20shepherds%20staged%20a%20protest%20in%20central%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Budgam%20district%20to%20denounce%20the%20%E2%80%9Chumiliating%20behaviour%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20forest%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20visit%20our%20homes%20and%20also%20break%20bread%20with%20us.%20Should%20he%20have%20humiliated%20us%20in%20this%20way%3F%20Shame%20on%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20shepherd%20protester%20can%20be%20heard%20saying%20in%20a%20video%20which%20was%20shared%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20and%20other%20social%20media%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20controversy%20refusing%20to%20die%2C%20the%20officer%20later%20issued%20a%20second%20order%2C%20withdrawing%20his%20remarks%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20word%20shepherd%20inadvertently%20crept%20(into%20the%20first%20order)%20is%20hereby%20expunged%20from%20the%20records.%20Further%20Range%20Officer%20Mawar%20is%20directed%20to%20expedite%20his%20enquiry%20report%20in%20the%20matter%20within%20five%20Divisional%20Forest%20Officer%2C%20Langate%20Forest%20Division%2C%20Langate%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20second%20order%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20chief%20minister%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Edemanded%20action%20against%20the%20officer.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20subsequent%20order%20smacks%20of%20prejudice%20towards%20our%20traditions%20by%20deriding%20him%20for%20%E2%80%98looking%20like%20a%20shepherd%E2%80%99.%20Are%20shepherds%20sub%20human%3F%20Insensitive%20%26amp%3B%20arrogant.%20Hope%20local%20admin%20takes%20action%20immediately%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20on%20X%2C%20tagging%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Sinha%20in%20her%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Pajwari%20said%20that%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Cfull%20of%20regret%E2%80%9D%20and%20apologised%20for%20hurting%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20shepherd%20community.%20%E2%80%9CI%20apologise%20for%20my%20remarks.%20I%20come%20from%20a%20backward%20caste%20myself.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20make%20distinctions%20between%20people%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20caste%2C%20creed%20or%20colour.%20I%20smell%20a%20political%20or%20departmental%20conspiracy%20in%20this%20issue%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20traditional%20cloak%2C%20which%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20introduced%20in%20the%20Valley%20by%20the%20Mughal%20emperor%20Akbar%2C%20has%20triggered%20a%20controversy%20in%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%20had%20called%20for%20imposing%20a%20ban%20on%20pherans%20after%20two%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20personnel%20were%20shot%20from%20point%20blank%20range%20in%20Srinagar.%20The%20attack%20was%20caught%20on%20camera%20and%20the%20attacker%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20a%20Lashkar-e-Tayyaba%20militant%2C%20had%20concealed%20an%20assault%20rifle%20under%20his%20pheran%20while%20moving%20towards%20the%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20a%20government%20order%20prohibiting%20officials%20from%20wearing%20pherans%20in%20official%20functions%20in%20north%20Kashmir%20was%20withdrawn%20following%20an%20uproar.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20order%20was%20also%20issued%20by%20an%20officer%20of%20the%20education%20department%20in%20the%20same%20Langate%20area%20where%20the%20fresh%20row%20has%20broken%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20the%20Army%20had%20asked%20the%20media%20not%20to%20wear%20pherans%20to%20press%20conferences%20for%20%E2%80%9Csecurity%20reasons%E2%80%9D%20which%20had%20also%20triggered%20outrage%20in%20Kashmir%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20pheran%20is%20a%20quintessential%20garment%20in%20Kashmiri%20wardrobes%20during%20winters%20when%20the%20temperature%20drops%20to%20sub-zero%20levels%2C%20with%20December%2021%20unofficially%20celebrated%20in%20the%20Valley%20as%20%E2%80%98International%20Pheran%20Day%E2%80%99%20to%20mark%20the%20arrival%20of%20Chilai%20Kalan%2C%20the%2040-day%20harshest%20winter%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20donned%20a%20pheren%20during%20his%20first%20visit%20to%20Kashmir%20as%20the%20PM%20in%202015%20while%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20also%20seen%20in%20a%20pheran%20when%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20arrived%20in%20Kashmir%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708498976000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21123154%2Fbrown-male-pheran.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fmet-with-outrage-jk-official-who-said-officer-wea