nghu%20Border%2C%20Tikri%20Border%2C%20and%20Ghazipur%20Border%20-%20are%20fortified%20with%20barricades%20made%20of%20barbed%20wire%2C%20nails%2C%20cement%2C%20and%20stone%20walls%2C%20supplemented%20by%20water%20cannons%20and%20anti-riot%20equipment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20imposition%20of%20security%20measures%20includes%20the%20deployment%20of%20long-range%20acoustic%20devices%20(LRAD)%2C%20producing%20unbearable%20noise%2C%20and%20the%20cancellation%20of%20all%20leaves%20for%20Delhi%20Police%20personnel.%20Historical%20landmarks%20like%20the%20Red%20Fort%20and%20India%20Gate%20have%20also%20been%20placed%20under%20heavy%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shambhu%20and%20Khanauri%20border%20points%20between%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20have%20become%20focal%20points%20of%20the%20ongoing%20standoff.%20Farmers%2C%20equipped%20with%20excavators%2C%20are%20determined%20to%20break%20through%20the%20barricades%20erected%20by%20Haryana%20security%20personnel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20four%20rounds%20of%20talks%20between%20farmer%20leaders%20and%20Union%20ministers%2C%20the%20stalemate%20continues.%20The%20recent%20rejection%20of%20the%20government's%20proposal%20to%20buy%20pulses%2C%20maize%2C%20and%20cotton%20crops%20at%20the%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20for%20five%20years%20has%20further%20fueled%20the%20resolve%20of%20the%20protesting%20farmers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20escalating%20tensions%2C%20the%20Haryana%20government%20has%20extended%20the%20ban%20on%20mobile%20internet%20and%20bulk%20text-message%20services%20in%20seven%20districts.%20Ambala%2C%20Kurukshetra%2C%20Kaithal%2C%20Jind%2C%20Hisar%2C%20Fatehabad%2C%20and%20Sirsa%20remain%20under%20these%20restrictions%2C%20emphasizing%20the%20government's%20concerns%20about%20maintaining%20law%20and%20order.%20Despite%20the%20confrontational%20atmosphere%2C%20farmer%20leaders%20insist%20on%20a%20peaceful%20march%20towards%20Delhi%20from%20the%20Shambhu%20and%