On%208%20February%2C%20a%20white%20paper%20on%20the%20Indian%20economy%20was%20tabled%20in%20the%20parliament%20in%20an%20apparent%20display%20of%20how%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20turned%20around%20a%20mismanaged%20economy%20they%20inherited.%20In%20the%20paper%2C%20a%20section%20on%20corruption%20is%20dedicated%20to%20the%20Rs.%201.86%20trillion%20coal%20block%20allocation%20scam%20under%20the%20previous%20Congress-led%20UPA%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20claims%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20took%20the%20country%20from%20%E2%80%9Cdarkness%20to%20light%20in%20coal%20licensing%E2%80%9D%20by%20ensuring%20%E2%80%9Ctransparent%20allocation%20of%20coal%20resources%E2%80%9D%20with%20its%20coal%20reforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20coal%20scam%20shook%20the%20conscience%20of%20the%20nation%20in%202014%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20paper%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20Modi-led%20BJP%20government%20ushered%20in%20a%20new%20coal%20auction%20and%20allocation%20regime%20to%20distribute%20more%20than%20200%20blocks%20of%20coal%20with%20over%2041%20billion%20tonnes%20of%20coal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Reporters%E2%80%99%20Collective%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0has%20found%2C%20contrary%20to%20claims%20the%20white%20paper%20makes%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20received%20early%20warnings%20that%20its%20own%20new%20coal%20regime%20was%20compromised%20and%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20lead%20to%20scams%E2%80%9D.%20These%20warnings%20came%20from%20two%20current%20Union%20ministers%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20trusts%2C%20who%20at%20the%20time%20of%20sending%20the%20missives%20were%20Parliamentarians%20%E2%80%93%20one%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20other%20supporting%20it%20as%20an%20independent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20cautioned%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Chastily%20drafted%E2%80%9D%20regulations%20to%20distribute%20India%E2%80%99s%20coal%20would%20allow%20private%20companies%20to%20rig%20auctions%20and%20corner%20huge%20benefits%20at%20a%20cost%