loads%2F2024%2F02%2F21094723%2FScreenshot-2024-02-21-at-9.41.30-AM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJalandhar%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20video%20of%20a%20Sikh%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20(IPS)%20officer%20posted%20in%20West%20Bengal%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20when%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20leader%20of%20opposition%20in%20the%20assembly%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20reportedly%20labelled%20him%20a%20%E2%80%98Khalistani%E2%80%99%20during%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20protest%20against%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20incident.%20Adhikari%E2%80%99s%20statement%20led%20to%20a%20major%20political%20controversy%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20legislators%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Adhikari%20were%20trying%20to%20enter%20Sandeshkhali%20village%20in%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district%2C%20when%20suddenly%20he%20accused%20IPS%20officer%20Jaspreet%20Singh%20of%20being%20a%20%E2%80%98Khalistani%E2%80%99.%20Singh%20is%20posted%20as%20Special%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(SSP)%2C%20Intelligence%20Branch%20(IB)%20at%20the%20Basirhat%20police%20station%2C%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20sooner%20did%20the%20video%20go%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20opposition%20parties%20slammed%20the%20BJP%20for%20its%20%E2%80%98anti-minority%E2%80%99%20stand%20and%20use%20of%20slurs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20BJP%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20Asansol%20South%20MLA%20Agnimitra%20Paul%20and%20Adhikari%20%E2%80%93%20figure%20prominently%20in%20the%20video%2C%20where%20they%20can%20be%20seen%20arguing%20with%20the%20police.%20The%20BJP%20is%20on%20the%20backfoot%3B%20its%20Punjab%20leadership%20is%20mum%20over%20the%20episode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Singh%20said%20he%20was%20on%20duty%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20village%20under%20the%20Basirhat%20police%20station%20when%20this%20incident%20took%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20Section%20144%20CrPC%20was%20in%20place%2C%20we%20tried%20to%20stop%20a%20group%20of%20politicians%20(BJP%20legislators)%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%2C%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Legislative%20Assembly%2C%20from%20entering%20Sandeshkhali.%20It%20was%20when%20we%20stopped%20the%20politicians%20that%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20called%20me%20%E2%80%98Khalistani%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20was%20totally%20unacceptable.%20I%20responded%20strongly%20against%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202016-batch%20IPS%20officer%20from%20Faridabad%2C%20Haryana%20said%20that%20when%20he%20confronted%20Adhikari%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader%20backed%20off%20and%20women%20leaders%20came%20to%20the%20forefront.%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20went%20behind%20and%20sat%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20message%20to%20minorities%2C%20particularly%20Sikhs%2C%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20growing%20instances%20of%20violence%20against%20them%2C%20Singh%20urged%20people%20not%20to%20consider%20themselves%20as%20%E2%80%98helpless%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98victims%E2%80%99.%20%E2%80%9CRather%2C%20be%20capable%20and%20strong%20enough%20to%20fight%20not%20only%20for%20yourself%20but%20for%20others%E2%80%99%20rights%20and%20dignity%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20expecting%20legal%20action%20soon.%20Our%20police%20team%20is%20examining%20the%20video%20footage%20and%20legal%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20as%20per%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20West%20Bengal%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20orders%20came%2C%20the%20police%20allowed%20the%20BJP%20legislators%20to%20enter%20Sandeshkhali%20at%20around%2012.30-1%20pm%2C%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20took%20place%20at%20a%20time%20when%20farmers%20%E2%80%93%20many%20of%20them%20Sikhs%20%E2%80%93%20who%20are%20making%20their%20way%20to%20Delhi%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20morcha%20were%20already%20being%20branded%20as%20%E2%80%98Khalistanis%E2%80%99%20and%20facing%20an%20onslaught%20on%20social%20media.%20Ever%20since%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20morcha%20began%20on%20February%2013%2C%20%E2%80%98Khalistanis%E2%80%99%20has%20been%20trending%20on%20social%20media%20site%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20video%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20Singh%20can%20be%20seen%20standing%20in%20the%20crowd%20and%20angrily%20responding%20to%20MLA%20Agnimitra%20Paul%20on%20the%20slur%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20take%20action%20on%20this.%20Just%20because%20I%20am%20wearing%20a%20turban%2C%20you%20labelled%20me%20a%20Khalistani%3F%20You%20cannot%20say%20anything%20about%20my%20religion.%20Has%20anybody%20said%20anything%20about%20your%20religion%3F%20Then%20why%20did%20you%20comment%20on%20my%20religion%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20officer%20then%20told%20Paul%20loudly%2C%20%E2%80%9CNobody%20is%20making%20any%20comments%20on%20religion%2C%20only%20you%20are%20making.%20If%20any%20police%20personnel%20are%20wearing%20a%20turban%2C%20will%20they%20be%20assumed%20to%20be%20Khalistanis%3F%20I%20am%20not%20discussing%20your%20faith%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20bring%20up%20mine%20either.%20How%20dare%20you%20label%20me%20a%20Khalistani!%20Is%20this%20your%20level%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20note%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Police%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20X%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Police%20fraternity%20are%20outraged%20to%20share%20the%20video%2C%20where%20one%20of%20our%20own%20officers%20was%20called%20%E2%80%98Khalistani%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Leader%20of%20Opposition.%20His%20%E2%80%98fault%E2%80%99%3A%20he%20is%20both%20a%20proud%20Sikh%20and%20a%20capable%20police%20officer%20who%20was%20trying%20to%20enforce%20the%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20comment%20is%20as%20much%20malicious%20and%20racial%20as%20it%20is%20communally%20inciting.%20It%20is%20a%20criminal%20act.%20We%20unequivocally%20condemn%20the%20unprovoked%2C%20unacceptable%20attack%20on%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20religious%20identity%20and%20beliefs%20aimed%20to%20incite%20people%20to%20take%20to%20violence%20and%20break%20the%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20police%20statement%20read.%20%E2%80%9CStern%20legal%20action%20is%20being%20initiated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20leaders%20slam%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%20and%20wrote%20on%20X%3A%20%E2%80%9CToday%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20divisive%20politics%20has%20shamelessly%20overstepped%20constitutional%20boundaries.%20As%20per%20BJP%20every%20person%20wearing%20a%20Turban%20is%20a%20Khalistani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20vehemently%20condemn%20this%20audacious%20attempt%20to%20undermine%20the%20reputation%20of%20our%20Sikh%20brothers%20and%20sisters%2C%20revered%20for%20their%20sacrifices%20and%20unwavering%20determination%20to%20our%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20stand%20firm%20in%20protecting%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20social%20harmony%20and%20will%20take%20stern%20lawful%20measures%20to%20prevent%20any%20attempts%20to%20disrupt%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20All-India%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20shared%20a%20video%20where%20Sikh%20community%20members%20held%20a%20protest%20raising%20%E2%80%98Kisan%20Virodhi%20BJP%2C%20Sikh%20Virodhi%20BJP%20murdabaad%E2%80%99%20slogans%20and%20wrote%20on%20X%3A%20%E2%80%9CMembers%20of%20the%20Sikh%20community%20staged%20a%20protest%20outside%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20party%20office%20demanding%20an%20apology%20for%20the%20communal%20slurs%20made%20by%20none%20other%20than%20the%20LoP%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20against%20an%20on%20duty%20IPS%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20them%2C%20every%20turban%20wearing%20man%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98Khalistani%E2%80%99.%20Apologise%20%40PM%20Narendra%20Modi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TMC%20also%20issued%20a%20press%20note%20in%20which%20it%20stated%20that%20sparking%20outrage%20across%20the%20nation%2C%20Adhikari%20on%20Tuesday%20perversely%20referred%20to%20an%20on-duty%20IPS%20officer%20as%20Khalistani%20while%20attempting%20to%20disturb%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20Sandeshkhali.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20a%20flagrant%20violation%20of%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%E2%80%99s%20directives%20which%20specifically%20prohibited%20the%20leader%20from%20issuing%20inflammatory%20speeches%20in%20the%20areas%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20addressing%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20AITC%20Mahila%20Wing%20president%20Chandrima%20Bhattacharya%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20country%20had%20not%20seen%20this%20level%20of%20divisive%20politics%20before%202014%2C%20the%20year%20BJP%20came%20to%20power.%20Since%20then%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20BJP%20engaging%20in%20such%20tactics%20multiple%20times.%20Even%20during%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests%2C%20they%20had%20deployed%20similar%20tactics.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shiromani%20Gurdwara%20Parbandhak%20Committee%20(SGPC)%20president%20Advocate%20Harjinder%20Singh%20Dhami%20expressed%20strong%20resentment%20against%20this%20incident%20and%20wrote%20on%20X%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20intentional%20character%20assassination%20of%20a%20Sikh%20IPS%20officer%20S.%20Jaspreet%20Singh%20by%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20in%20West%20Bengal%20is%20highly%20condemnable.%20Leaders%20who%20have%20such%20thinking%20in%20the%20country%20should%20never%20forget%20that%20Sikhs%20have%20made%20the%20most%20sacrifices%20for%20the%20freedom%20and%20protection%20of%20the%20country.%20Sikhs%20do%20not%20need%20a%20certificate%20from%20anyone%2C%20rather%20they%20know%20how%20to%20perform%20services%20for%20the%20nation%20in%20accordance%20with%20their%20traditions%20and%20customs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhami%20also%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20big%20question%20that%20such%20people%20in%20the%20country%20deliberately%20create%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20hatred%20but%20the%20governments%20remain%20silent.%20Those%20who%20create%20such%20an%20atmosphere%20should%20be%20punished%20so%20that%20people%20who%20are%20honestly%20doing%20their%20duty%20in%20different%20areas%20do%20not%20have%20to%20be%20victims%20of%20such%20hate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20opposition%20in%20the%20Punjab%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20and%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Partap%20Singh%20Bajwa%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20shameful%20beyond%20words.%20BJP%20workers%20in%20West%20Bengal%20are%20calling%20a%20Sikh%20IPS%20officer%20Khalistani%20just%20because%20he%20is%20doing%20his%20duty.%20Is%20this%20what%20BJP%20thinks%20about%20the%20Sikhs%3F%20A%20strong%20action%20should%20be%20taken%20against%20those%20trying%20to%20create%20this%20hooliganism%20and%20portraying%20Sikhs%20as%20Khalistanis.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20spokesperson%20Daljit%20Singh%20Cheema%20also%20slammed%20the%20BJP%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CLabelling%20a%20decorated%20Sikh%20Police%20officer%20as%20Khalistani%20who%20was%20performing%20bonafide%20duties%20as%20police%20officer%20in%20West%20Bengal%20is%20strongly%20condemnable%2C%20highly%20objectionable%20and%20a%20case%20of%20serious%20hate%20crime.%20A%20case%20should%20be%20registered%20against%20the%20culprit%20and%20the%20guilty%20must%20be%20given%20exemplary%20punishment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708489186000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21094723%2FScreenshot-2024-02-21-at-9.41.30-AM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Ftotally-unacceptable-sikh-ips-officer-called-khalistani-by-bjps-suvendu-adhikari%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BJP%20leaders%20who%20were%20stopped%20on%20the%20wa