4%2F02%2F20144212%2FIMG_2915-1-746x1024.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22271%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20144212%2FIMG_2915-1-746x1024.jpg%20746w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20144212%2FIMG_2915-1-219x300.jpg%20219w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20144212%2FIMG_2915-1.jpg%20874w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697965%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22372%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty.%20Photo%3A%20Intifada%20P.%20Basheer%20and%20Azam%20Abbas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20Sales%20Pulse%20data%20compiled%20by%20%3Cem%3EHowIndiaLives%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20delves%20into%20an%20analysis%20of%20how%20Indians%20are%20managing%20to%20sustain%20themselves%20with%20their%20current%20jobs%2C%20rather%20than%20thriving%20under%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pmindia.gov.in%2Fen%2Fnews_updates%2Fpm-to-launch-viksit-bharat-2047-voice-of-youth-on-11th-december%2F%5C%22%3EViksit%20Bharat%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20if%20FMCG%20sales%20are%20sluggish%2C%20household%20savings%20are%20declining%2C%20and%20borrowing%20levels%20are%20soaring%2C%20it%20may%20suggest%20that%20workers%20are%20facing%20challenges%20in%20sustaining%20their%20living%20standards%20and%20may%20be%20merely%20surviving%20rather%20than%20thriving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20a%20lack%20of%20data%20also%20hampers%20the%20measurement%20of%20how%20an%20economy%20consumes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20trouble%20is%20we%20haven%E2%80%99t%20had%20a%20consumption%20survey.%20There%20was%20a%20consumption%20survey%20for%202017-18%2C%20but%20the%20government%20ditched%20that%20one%20because%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20like%20the%20results.%20A%20leaked%20version%20of%20that%20survey%20showed%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fconsumer-sending-fall-rural-demand-nso-report%5C%22%3Erural%20consumption%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20actually%20fallen%20over%20that%20six-year%20period%2C%20from%202011-12%20to%202017-18.%20And%20since%20then%20they%20have%20not%20had%20a%20consumption%20survey.%20They%E2%80%99re%20supposed%20to%20be%20doing%20one%20now%2C%20but%20we%E2%80%99ll%20not%20get%20those%20results%20for%20at%20least%20another%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20renowned%20development%20economist%20Jayati%20Ghosh%20said%2C%20while%20speaking%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Eon%20whether%20Indian%20workers%20are%20thriving%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fblogs%2Fmyview%2Findia-under-pm-modi-poised-to-become-a-5-trillion-economy-in-5-years%2F%5C%22%3Egrowing%20GDP%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20merely%20surviving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20why%20would%20you%20not%20do%20a%20consumption%20survey%3F%20Because%20those%20surveys%20tell%20us%20how%20many%20poor%20people%20are%20there%20are%20in%20the%20country%2C%20where%20they%20are%2C%20what%20they%20do%3B%20they%20%5Bthese%20surveys%5D%20tell%20us%20about%20distribution%2C%20because%20these%20give%20us%20some%20indication%20of%20who%20can%20consume%20what%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20other%20survey%20which%20is%20%5Balso%5D%20a%20better%20indicator%20is%20the%20labour%20force%20survey.%20The%20government%20has%20allowed%20that%20survey%20to%20continue%2C%20but%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20long%20they%20will%2C%20because%20that%20has%20also%20not%20shown%20good%20results%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20further%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20%5BThe%20labour%20force%20survey%5D%20shows%20us%20that%20real%20wages%20are%20more%20or%20less%20stagnating.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNote%20that%20these%20are%20average%20real%20wages%20and%20these%20can%20get%20distorted%20at%20the%20upper%20end%2C%20and%20make%20it%20look%20higher.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20if%20we%20really%20want%20to%20know%20how%20workers%20are%20doing%2C%20we%20should%20be%20looking%20at%20the%20median%20wages%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20many%20countries%20do.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20look%20at%20the%20median%20wages.%20That%20is%2C%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20distribution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20average%20wages%20are%20stagnating%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20quite%20possible%20that%20the%20median%20wages%20have%20actually%20come%20down%20in%20real%20terms.%20Some%20people%20are%20actually%20working%20on%20this%20data%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20the%20average%20can%20be%20skewed%20by%20outliers%2C%20especially%20if%20there%20are%20significant%20income%20disparities%20within%20the%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Funpaid-labour-on-the-rise-muslims-not-looking-for-work-what-the-plfs-data-reveals%5C%22%3EUnpaid%20Labour%20on%20the%20Rise%2C%20Muslims%20Not%20Looking%20for%20Work%3A%20What%20the%20PLFS%20Data%20Reveals%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20interesting%20sets%20of%20data%20%E2%80%93%20vehicle%20registrations%20and%20provident%20fund%20distribution%20by%20large%2C%20medium%20and%20small%20firms%20%E2%80%93%20that%20could%20give%20a%20glimpse%20of%20the%20economic%20well-being%20of%20the%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20used%20to%20create%20the%20charts%20below%20is%20as%20of%20February%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFluctuations%20in%20two-wheelers%2C%20steady%20growth%20in%20hybrid%20and%20electric%20vehicles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVehicle%20registrations%20are%20also%20considered%20a%20proxy%20for%20retail%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo-wheeler%20sales%20data%20are%20often%20considered%20a%20key%20indicator%20of%20consumption%20demand%2C%20especially%20in%20countries%20like%20India%20where%20they%20are%20a%20popular%20mode%20of%20transportation.%20They%20indicate%20the%20purchasing%20capacity%20of%20the%20middle%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20shows%20that%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdown%2C%20registrations%20of%20two-wheelers%20dropped%20to%20161%2C314%20units%20in%20May%202020%20and%20kept%20fluctuating%20until%20January%202023.%20They%20appear%20to%20have%20been%20recovering%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20on%20September%2030%2C%202023%2C%20they%20stood%20at%201.31%20million%20units%2C%20higher%20than%201.16%20million%20units%20in%20the%20same%20period%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20clearly%20reaches%20its%20peak%20in%20the%20month%20of%20November%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20noteworthy%20here%20is%20the%20intensity%20of%20the%20dip%20during%20the%20pandemic%20and%20the%20fluctuations%20thereafter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20take%20a%20look%20at%20the%20registrations%20of%20hybrid%20vehicles%20within%20the%20renewable%20category%20and%20electric%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fh8Wd8%2F1%2F%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Two-wheeler%20sales%3A%20A%20rollercoaster%20ride%20from%20lockdown%20lows%20to%20recovery%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVehicle%20registrations%20in%20the%20renewable%20category%20(see%20below)%20show%20a%20steady%20rise.%20As%20earlier%20mentioned%2C%20this%20category%20includes%20hybrid%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20hybrid%20vehicles%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fauto.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpassenger-vehicle%2Fare-hybrid-vehicles-better-than-electric-vehicles%2F104908025%5C%22%3Etend%20to%20be%20more%20expensive%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20compared%20to%20their%20conventional%20counterparts.%20Hybrid%20cars%20also%20require%20more%20maintenance%20than%20the%20conventional%20ones.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20question%20is%2C%20how%20many%20people%20from%20the%20middle%20class%20and%20lower-middle%20class%20can%20afford%20buying%20hybrid%20models%20of%20cars%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20luxury%20cars%20are%20also%20doing%20well%20and%20not%20just%20the%20EVs.%20EVs%20are%20definitely%20expensive.%20And%20so%20are%20hybrid%20%5Bvehicles%5D.%20They%20are%20all%20much%20more%20%5Bexpensive%5D%20than%20the%20regular%20%5Bvehicles%5D.%20But%20all%20luxury%20vehicles%20are%20doing%20well.%20So%2C%20that%20tells%20you%20exactly%20who%E2%80%99s%20gaining%20from%20all%20this%20growth%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ghosh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Frenewables%2Findia-sees-over-120-growth-in-evs-hybrid-vehicles-surge-400%2Farticleshow%2F102895037.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3ENews%20agency%20IANS%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20a%20report%20by%20Cyber%20Media%20Research%2C%20said%20that%20India%20saw%20a%20120%25%20growth%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%202023%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20400%25%20surge%20in%20hybrid%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FvGlm2%2F1%2F%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Vehicle%20registrations%20within%20the%20renewable%20category%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20in%20the%20chart%20below%2C%20registrations%20of%20electric%20(battery%20operated)%20vehicles%20peaked%20when%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdown%20had%20started.%20After%20the%20pandemic%2C%20the%20demand%20has%20consistently%20risen.%20Their%20adoption%2C%20especially%20at%20a%20time%20when%20over%20120%20million%20people%20in%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fdata%2Fdata-over-12-crore-indians-lost-their-jobs-during-the-coronavirus-lockdown-in-april%2Farticle61660110.ece%5C%22%3Elost%20their%20jobs%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20indicate%20stark%20economic%20disparities%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FOD2bc%2F1%2F%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Electric%20vehicles%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20than%20EV%20sales%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenergy.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpower%2Findias-ev-sales-surge-to-1-5-million-in-2023-up-50-report%2F106971357%5C%22%3Ehave%20been%20revving%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20despite%20concerns%20over%20a%20lack%20of%20charging%20stations%20and%20policy%20roadblocks.%20But%20again%2C%20which%20segment%20of%20the%20population%20buys%20EVs%20and%20hybrid%20vehicles%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20remarkable%20surge%20in%20luxury%20cars%20shows%20that%20the%20purchasing%20power%20of%20these%20buyers%20has%20grown%20exponentially%2C%20and%20they%20are%20not%20hesitating%20to%20spend%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20to%20Rs%201%20crore%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fmultimedia%2Faudio%2Fwhat-is-driving-indias-luxury-car-market-boom%2Farticle67344022.ece%5C%22%3EState%20of%20The%20Economy%20podcast%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20luxury%20car%20market%20growth.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERural%20demand%20weakness%20in%20FMCG%20sector%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20fast-moving%20consumer%20goods%20(FMCG)%20sales%20serve%20as%20a%20crucial%20indicator%20of%20consumption%20demand%20in%20an%20economy.%20These%20include%20sales%20of%20items%20such%20as%20toothpaste%2C%20biscuits%2C%20detergents%2C%20dairy%20products%2C%20personal%20care%20products%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChanges%20observed%20in%20FMCG%20sales%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20changes%20in%20economic%20conditions%2C%20such%20as%20fluctuations%20in%20income%20levels%2C%20employment%20rates%2C%20and%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Findustry%2Fretail%2Ffmcg-sector-rural-demand-weakness-drags-q3-revenue-growth-prefer-itc-emami-asian-paints-britannia-centrum-broking-11708061442224.html%5C%22%3Erural%20demand%20weakness%3C%2Fa%3E%20dragged%20FMCG%20companies%E2%80%99%20revenue%20growth%20in%20the%20October-December%20quarter%20of%20financial%20year%202024.%20Volume%20growth%20remained%20muted%20for%20hair%20oil%2C%20health%20and%20food%20drinks%2C%20and%20beauty%20and%20personal%20care%20segments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbctv18.com%2Fbusiness%2Ffmcg-sector-outlook-growth-nielsen-18991571.htm%5C%22%3ENielsenIQ%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20FMCG%20sector%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Ffmcg-growth-slows-sequentially-in-december-quarter-expected-to-slow-to-4-5-6-5-in-2024-report%5C%22%3Eis%20expected%20to%20grow%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%204.5-6.5%25%20in%202024%2C%20sharply%20lower%20than%20the%20robust%209.3%25%20growth%20experienced%20in%202023%20and%208.4%25%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fmore-inventory-days-for-consumer-goods-as-low-demand-causes-supply-chain-congestion%5C%22%3Ehad%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20November%20that%20persistent%20low%20demand%20in%20the%20FMCG%20sector%20is%20causing%20supply%20chain%20congestion%2C%20leading%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20inventory%20days%2C%20with%20stocks%20accumulating%20at%20distributors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20big%20companies%20such%20as%20Hindustan%20Unilever%20and%20Dabur%20have%20also%20said%20that%20the%20rural%20markets%20are%20lagging%20urban.%20Many%20have%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Feconomy%2Frural-demand-revival-what-new-data-tells-us-11698085155203.html%5C%22%3Eraised%20doubts%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20a%20revival%20in%20rural%20demand%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMedium-sized%20firms%20saw%20sharp%20decline%20in%20PF%20contributions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProvident%20Fund%20(PF)%20contributions%20by%20large%2C%20medium%20and%20small%20firms%20reflect%20how%20people%20save%20in%20an%20economy.%20It%20could%20also%20be%20an%20indicator%20of%20social%20security%20within%20an%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20data%20is%20a%20good%20indicator%20on%20how%20workers%20are%20doing%20in%20an%20economy.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20when%20you%20register%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20say%2C%20for%20the%20EPF%2C%20you%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20do%20anything%20with%20monthly%20payment%2C%20especially%20when%20you%20change%20jobs.%20%5BMany%20time%5D%20workers%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20%5Bthey%20have%20an%20EPF%5D%2C%20and%20it%20gets%20dropped%20from%20their%20pay%20when%20they%20join%20another%20firm%2C%20and%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20portable.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20necessarily%20carry%20it%20with%20them.%20So%2C%20they%20actually%20lose.%20It%E2%80%99s%20like%20a%20tax%20on%20their%20wage%20rather%20than%20actually%20savings%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ghosh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSecondly%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20not%20doing%20the%20surveys%20that%20they%20should%20be.%20There%20was%20an%20all-India%20Debt%20and%20Investment%20survey%2C%20which%20was%20due%2C%20which%20would%20give%20us%20an%20idea%20about%20household%20savings.%20And%20how%20much%20dissavings%20happens%20at%20the%20lower%20level.%20So%2C%20they%20%5Bthe%20government%5D%20are%20not%20collecting%20the%20important%20data%20that%20wold%20give%20us%20this%20information%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%2C%20what%20you%E2%80%99ve%20just%20described%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20PF%20of%20the%20large%20firms%20versus%20the%20others%20%5Bmedium%20and%20small%20firms%5D%2C%20it%20speaks%20very%20much%20of%20the%20broader%20picture%20that%20is%20coming%20out%20of%20corporate%20profitability%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20professor%20pointed%20out%20a%20report%20which%20said%20that%2090%25%20of%20the%20corporate%20profit%20in%20India%20was%20made%20by%20the%20top%20few%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20top%2020%20profit%20generators%20in%20India%20(%E2%80%9Cthe%20Leviathans%E2%80%9D)%20now%20account%20for%2090%25%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20corporate%20profits.%20Beyond%20dominating%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20profit%20pool%2C%20the%20Leviathans%20also%20reinvest%20these%20profits%20far%20more%20efficiently%20back%20into%20their%20businesses%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarcellus.in%2Fblogs%2Findias-top-20-leviathans-awe-inspiring-dominance%2F%5C%22%3EMarcellus%20Investment%20Managers%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20May%202020.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20reduced%20profitability%2C%20and%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20negative%20profitability.%20And%20we%20know%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20of%20churning%20in%20the%20small%20and%20micro%20enterprises.%20Some%20are%20closing%20down%20and%20then%20people%20start%20something%20else%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20three%20charts%20below%2C%20it%20is%20evident%20that%20PF%20contributions%20by%20all%20firms%20experienced%20a%20significant%20decline%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20The%20most%20pronounced%20fall%2C%20as%20illustrated%20by%20the%20curve%2C%20occurred%20in%20medium-sized%20firms%2C%20whereas%20the%20drop%20in%20PF%20contributions%20from%20large%20firms%20appears%20less%20steep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20graphs%20are%20consistent%20for%20both%20small%20and%20medium%20firms%2C%20PF%20amounts%20paid%20by%20large%20firms%20show%20a%20sharp%20increa